<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title><%= title %> - Sistem Komoditas</title>
  
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.11.0/font/bootstrap-icons.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
  
  <style>
    * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
    body { font-family: 'Segoe UI', 'Roboto', sans-serif; overflow-x: hidden; }
    
    .auth-container {
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    
    .auth-form-side {
      flex: 1;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: 40px 20px;
      background: white;
      z-index: 2;
    }
    
    .auth-visual-side {
      flex: 1;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #9CAB88 0%, #89986D 50%, #C5D89D 100%);
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
      display: none;
    }
    
    @media (min-width: 992px) {
      .auth-visual-side { display: block; }
    }
    
    .bg-shapes { position: absolute; width: 100%; height: 100%; overflow: hidden; }
    .shape {
      position: absolute;
      opacity: 0.1;
      animation: float 20s infinite ease-in-out;
    }
    
    .shape-1 {
      width: 300px;height: 300px;
      background: white;
      border-radius: 50%;
      top: -100px;
      right: -100px;
      animation-delay: 0s;
    }
    
    .shape-2 {
      width: 200px;
      height: 200px;
      background: white;
      border-radius: 30% 70% 70% 30% / 30% 30% 70% 70%;
      bottom: 100px;
      left: -50px;
      animation-delay: 3s;
    }
    
    .shape-3 {
      width: 150px;
      height: 150px;
      background: white;
      border-radius: 50%;
      top: 50%;
      right: 20%;
      animation-delay: 6s;
    }
    
    @keyframes float {
      0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0) rotate(0deg); }
      25% { transform: translateY(-20px) rotate(5deg); }
      50% { transform: translateY(0) rotate(0deg); }
      75% { transform: translateY(20px) rotate(-5deg); }
    }
    
    .visual-content {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 2;
      color: white;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 60px;
      height: 100%;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: center;
    }
    
    .visual-content h1 {
      font-size: 48px;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      animation: slideInRight 1s ease-out;
    }
    
    .visual-content p {
      font-size: 20px;
      opacity: 0.95;
      line-height: 1.6;
      animation: slideInRight 1s ease-out 0.2s both;
    }
    
    .visual-icon {
      font-size: 120px;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
      animation: bounceIn 1s ease-out;
    }
    
    .form-container {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 460px;
      animation: fadeInUp 0.8s ease-out;
    }
    
    .logo-section {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 40px;
    }
    
    .logo-icon {
      font-size: 60px;
      color: #9CAB88;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
      animation: pulse 2s ease-in-out infinite;
    }
    
    .logo-section h2 {
      font-size: 32px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #2c3e50;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }
    
    .logo-section p {
      color: #7f8c8d;
      font-size: 15px;
    }
    
    .form-control {
      padding: 14px 16px;
      font-size: 15px;
      border: 2px solid #e0e0e0;
      border-radius: 8px;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
    }
    
    .form-control:focus {
      border-color: #9CAB88;
      box-shadow: 0 0 0 4px rgba(156, 171, 136, 0.15);
    }
    
    .input-group { position: relative; }
    .input-icon {
      position: absolute;
      left: 16px;
      top: 50%;
      transform: translateY(-50%);
      color: #7f8c8d;
      font-size: 18px;
      z-index: 10;
    }
    
    .input-group .form-control { padding-left: 48px; }
    
    .btn-auth {
      padding: 14px;
      font-size: 16px;
      font-weight: 600;
      border-radius: 8px;
      border: none;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #9CAB88 0%, #89986D 100%);
      color: white;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(156, 171, 136, 0.3);
    }
    
    .btn-auth:hover {
      transform: translateY(-2px);
      box-shadow: 0 6px 16px rgba(156, 171, 136, 0.4);
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #89986D 0%, #9CAB88 100%);
    }
    
    .divider {
      text-align: center;
      margin: 24px 0;
      position: relative;
    }
    
    .divider::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      left: 0;
      top: 50%;
      width: 100%;
      height: 1px;
      background: #e0e0e0;
    }
    
    .divider span {
      background: white;
      padding: 0 16px;
      color: #7f8c8d;
      font-size: 14px;
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
    }
    
    .switch-link {
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 24px;
      color: #7f8c8d;
      font-size: 15px;
    }
    
    .switch-link a {
      color: #9CAB88;
      font-weight: 600;
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
    }
    
    .switch-link a:hover {
      color: #89986D;
      text-decoration: underline;
    }
    
    .alert {
      border-radius: 8px;
      border: none;
      padding: 14px 18px;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
      animation: slideInDown 0.4s ease-out;
    }
    
    .alert-success {
      background: #e8f5e9;
      color: #2e7d32;
      border-left: 4px solid #4caf50;
    }
    
    .alert-danger {
      background: #ffebee;
      color: #c62828;
      border-left: 4px solid #f44336;
    }
    
    @keyframes fadeInUp {
      from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(30px); }
      to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
    }
    
    @keyframes slideInRight {
      from { opacity: 0; transform: translateX(50px); }
      to { opacity: 1; transform: translateX(0); }
    }
    
    @keyframes slideInDown {
      from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(-20px); }
      to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
    }
    
    @keyframes bounceIn {
      0% { opacity: 0; transform: scale(0.3); }
      50% { opacity: 1; transform: scale(1.05); }
      70% { transform: scale(0.9); }
      100% { transform: scale(1); }
    }
    
    @keyframes pulse {
      0%, 100% { transform: scale(1); }
      50% { transform: scale(1.1); }
    }
    
    @media (max-width: 991px) {
      .auth-form-side { padding: 30px 20px; }
      .form-container { max-width: 100%; }
      .logo-section h2 { font-size: 28px; }
    }
    
    @media (max-width: 576px) {
      .logo-section h2 { font-size: 24px; }
      .logo-icon { font-size: 50px; }
      .form-control { padding: 12px 14px; font-size: 14px; }
      .input-group .form-control { padding-left: 44px; }
      .visual-content h1 { font-size: 32px; }
      .visual-content p { font-size: 16px; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="auth-container">
    <div class="auth-form-side">
      <div class="form-container">
        <div class="logo-section">
          <div class="logo-icon">
            <i class="bi bi-box-seam"></i>
          </div>
          <h2>Selamat Datang!</h2>
          <p>Masuk ke Sistem Manajemen Komoditas</p>
        </div>

        <% if (locals.success && success.length > 0) { %>
          <div class="alert alert-success alert-dismissible fade show">
            <i class="bi bi-check-circle me-2"></i><%= success %>
            <button type="button" class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="alert"></button>
          </div>
        <% } %>

        <% if (locals.error && error.length > 0) { %>
          <div class="alert alert-danger alert-dismissible fade show">
            <i class="bi bi-exclamation-circle me-2"></i><%= error %>
            <button type="button" class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="alert"></button>
          </div>
        <% } %>

        <form action="/login" method="POST">
          <div class="mb-3">
            <label for="email" class="form-label">Email</label>
            <div class="input-group">
              <i class="bi bi-envelope input-icon"></i>
              <input type="email" class="form-control" id="email" name="email" 
                     placeholder="Masukkan email" required autofocus>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="mb-4">
            <label for="password" class="form-label">Password</label>
            <div class="input-group">
              <i class="bi bi-lock input-icon"></i>
              <input type="password" class="form-control" id="password" name="password" 
                     placeholder="Masukkan password" required>
            </div>
          </div>

          <button type="submit" class="btn btn-auth w-100">
            <i class="bi bi-box-arrow-in-right me-2"></i>Masuk
          </button>
        </form>

        <div class="text-center mt-3">
          <a href="/forgot-password" style="color: #9CAB88; font-weight: 600; text-decoration: none;">
            Lupa password?
          </a>
        </div>

        <div class="divider"><span>atau</span></div>

        <div class="switch-link">
          Belum punya akun? <a href="/register">Daftar Sekarang</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="auth-visual-side">
      <div class="bg-shapes">
        <div class="shape shape-1"></div>
        <div class="shape shape-2"></div>
        <div class="shape shape-3"></div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="visual-content">
        <div class="visual-icon">
          <i class="bi bi-graph-up-arrow"></i>
        </div>
        <h1>Sistem Manajemen<br>Komoditas Terpadu</h1>
        <p>Kelola komoditas, formulasi pangan, analisis gizi,<br>
           hingga distribusi dalam satu platform modern</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
  <script>
    setTimeout(() => {
      document.querySelectorAll('.alert').forEach(alert => {
        new bootstrap.Alert(alert).close();
      });
    }, 5000);
  </script>
</body>
</html>
